Ques.2. A shop will give discount of 10% if the cost of purchased quantity is more than 1000.
Ask user for quantity
Suppose, one unit will cost 100.
Judge and print total cost for user.
import java.util.Scanner;
public class App {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.println("Enter quantity of articles: ");
		int qty = sc.nextInt();
		
		int total = 100*qty;
		
		int discount = (10*total)/100;
		
		int amount = total-discount; 
		
		if (qty>10) {
			System.out.println("After 10% discount and the amount you have to pay:- "+amount);
		}
		else {
			System.out.println("You have to pay: "+total);
		}
	}

